It&#8217;s understood a staff member at the casino found the body in a dam at the property while working on Wednesday morning. JOHANNESBURG A body has been found at Montecasino.It s understood a staff member at the casino found the body in a dam at the property while working on Wednesday morning.Police say they were not able to identify the body as it's in a decomposed state.The police's Mpho Khaswane says the circumstance surrounding the death are not yet clear. At about 10am this morning the police received information about a body that had been discovered at Montecasino, in the dam. It s a man, aged between 30 and 35. In 2013, a body was found in the boot of a car at Montecasino.Two people were found guilty of murder and received lengthy prison sentences.(Edited by Masechaba Sefularo)